{"tid":2358457,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸收緊互聯網法規 就疫情、災情、藥物安全發佈假信息 由尋釁滋事提升至國安法水平","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T15:27:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"21e4d18347d77575cd3ea834b34613d0ff817063","tid":2358457,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"內地互聯網管理修訂草案 禁止煽動顛覆國家政權等內容<br />\n<br />\n內地《互聯網信息服務管理辦法》修訂草案的徵求意見稿規定，從事互聯網信息服務的境內組織和個人，不得製作、複製、發布、傳播9項信息，否則罰款1萬至100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n國家網信辦今日至下月7日公開徵求意見。其中草案第26條規定，不得編造、傳播險情、疫情、警情、自然災害、生產安全、食品藥品等產品安全和其他擾亂社會秩序的虛假信息。<br />\n<br />\n草案亦禁止有關反對憲法確定的基本原則，危害國家安全，煽動顛覆國家政權，煽動分裂國家，破壞國家統一等內容。至於散布煽動非法集會、結社、遊行、示威等信息亦被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569350-20210108.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569350-20210108.htm&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIdw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=e66bc7eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569350-20210108.htm&h=f2629529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569350-20210108.htm</a>"},{"pid":"418deea880370a0f928d3111d35e1a4bad6bb760","tid":2358457,"uid":55913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人是需要管的"},{"pid":"9e4c6eb0d1b754cb3bab98b555e4c338a9d34a49","tid":2358457,"uid":152476,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"總之中國無事<br />\n外國好撚亂仆晒街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8353f6761741148a5d45075509b2b0b08a5bb4f2","tid":2358457,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"香港死撚梗"},{"pid":"eb0a6e757d30b982a1a28b46d1e1afb00eb73144","tid":2358457,"uid":23635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":